TextBody:
Hi Oscar,

Okay, if that is the case, we create two snapshots per day, so you don't really need that backup for now. If it does not finish by the end of today's work day, let me know and I will request access to your backend. If you allow me to connect in your absence I can check and let you know what I find.
I will also ask our server team if we can cancel the backup process.
Please let me know if that works for you.

Thank you,
Eduard Nut
Technical Support Engineer

Hi Oscar,

Okay, if that is the case, we create two snapshots per day, so you don't really need that backup for now. If it does not finish by the end of today's work day, let me know and I will request access to your backend. If you allow me to connect in your absence I can check and let you know what I find.
I will also ask our server team if we can cancel the backup process.
Please let me know if that works for you.

Thank you,
